[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cameron Burgess: Oldham Athletic sign Fulham defender on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
League One side Oldham Athletic have signed Fulham defender Cameron Burgess club on loan until 5 January.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The centre-back, 20, spent time in the youth system at Celtic and Aberdeen before his family moved to Australia.
He then switched his allegiance to Australia at international level and has played for their Under-23 side.
"Cameron is a left-sided centre-half who will give us a lot of physique and experience," boss Stephen Robinson told the club website.
